    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This 2004 Honda S2000 (AP2) is a superlative example of high-revving atmospheric engineering. Powered by the F22C1 inline-four, the powerplant delivers a linear power band with VTEC engagement at 6,000 RPM, strictly maintained with OEM filters and full-synthetic lubricants. The longitudinal 6-speed manual transmission features crisp, short-throw gates with flawless synchros. Chassis rigidity is absolute, featuring the legendary double-wishbone suspension geometry and a Torsen helical limited-slip differential for optimal torque biasing. All factory VIN tags are present on body panels, confirming an accident-free history. This unit exhibits zero subframe oxidation and retains its factory-spec alignment settings. A true collector-grade specimen for the driving purist.",
