      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage and driven only on fair-weather weekends. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with a professional ceramic coating applied annually; there are zero stone chips, swirl marks, or blemishes to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in a 'time-capsule' state\u2014the leather is supple with no bolster wear, the carpets have been protected by double-layer mats since day one, and all electronics function with factory precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive binder of service records from the original dealership. Recent preventative maintenance includes a full fluid flush and a multi-point inspection, confirming its flawless status. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks, smells, and drives exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
